Official package hub/repository

rust|crates.io
python|PyPI

package manager

rust|cargo
JS|npm (technically for node, but commonly used for anything)
Ubuntu|apt
macOS|brew|port

Package manifest

rust|Cargo.toml

update|update the package index|brew|npm
upgrade|installs all available updates|brew|npm
install PACKAGE|install a package|apt|brew|npm
uninstall PACKAGE|uninstall a package|brew|npm
remove PACKAGE|uninstall a package|apt
ls/list|list installed packages|brew|npm
outdated|show a list of outdated packages|brew|npm
tap TAPNAME|add a repository|brew